MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2008-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 20th October, 2008
28 Asvina, 1930 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 18th
October, 2008, Shri Anand Sharma assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of State in the Ministry of Information and Broadcasting. He will
continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of External Affairs.
(S.K. Valiathan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5344
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of
the Planning Commission.
